data.description: Welcome to charming bungalow living in Monroe. Nestled on a spacious .25-acre lot less than a mile from the vibrant downtown Monroe, this fully renovated 2 bedrooms, 1 bath bungalow offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and classic charm. Step into a world of modern elegance with this home which underwent a full renovation in 2020. From the gleaming granite countertops to the stainless-steel appliances, every detail exudes quality craftsmanship and contemporary style. Enjoy peace of mind knowing that the roof and all systems are less than 3 years old. You don't want to miss this one!!
